      <title>瑞士央行对在其货币储备中持有比特币持怀疑态度</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/swiss-national-bank-sceptical-bitcoin-its-currency-reserves-2024-04-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士国家银行主席托马斯乔丹周五表示，尽管活动人士呼吁修改瑞士法律并允许加密货币加入其货币储备，但瑞士国家银行仍然对购买比特币持怀疑态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/swiss-national-bank-sceptical-bitcoin-its-currency-reserves-2024-04-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 11:32:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯将从7月起提高无担保消费贷款的风险溢价</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russia-raise-risk-premiums-unsecured-consumer-loans-july-2024-04-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯央行周五表示，将从7月1日起提高无担保消费贷款的风险溢价，以减轻公民的债务负担，并在消费贷款损失增加的情况下提高银行业的稳定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russia-raise-risk-premiums-unsecured-consumer-loans-july-2024-04-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 11:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
